{"tid":866523,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[Once you go black] 歷史首次！曼城球星孔帕尼父親成為比利時首位黑人市長","createTime":"2018-10-18T02:47:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-18T14:49:23.000Z","uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"488d142c138840aaa184c48425e642d535857795","tid":866523,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T02:47:11.000Z","msg":"歷史首次！孔帕尼父親成為比利時首位黑人市長<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://sports.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/2584045?fbclid=IwAR1wN8KPdwiIje0PFI1LsWuAbKRRSvRunMLm6oaCyrww0L-f5ksHOfJK6vk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsports.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F2584045%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1wN8KPdwiIje0PFI1LsWuAbKRRSvRunMLm6oaCyrww0L-f5ksHOfJK6vk&d=u4stnqq8vOcMSVos4gNuvaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=14886dca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsports.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F2584045%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1wN8KPdwiIje0PFI1LsWuAbKRRSvRunMLm6oaCyrww0L-f5ksHOfJK6vk&h=3b49ddd7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://sports.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/2584045?fbclid=IwAR1wN8KPdwiIje0PFI1LsWuAbKRRSvRunMLm6oaCyrww0L-f5ksHOfJK6vk</a><br />\n<br />\n〔體育中心／綜合報導〕曼城球星孔帕尼（Vincent Kompany）昨傳出好消息，他的父親皮埃爾‧孔帕尼（Pierre Kompany）當選比利時漢斯霍倫市的市長，同時也是比利時歷史上首位黑人市長。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n出生於剛果民主共和國的皮埃爾，早年為了躲避戰亂，舉家遷移至歐洲，最後在比利時定居。由於對政治充滿理想，最後他放棄機械工程師的工作，投身於政治，並在2014年6月成為了布魯塞爾首都大區議會議員，4年後更成為了市長。根據法媒《隊報》的報導，皮埃爾在市長選舉中拿到了28.38%的支持率，成為了比利時的首位黑人市長。</span><br />\n<br />\n孔帕尼也在Instagram上祝賀了爸爸，他說：「這是歷史性的一刻！父親，我們為你感到驕傲。1975年以難民的身分來到比利時，但是現在成為了比利時歷史上首位黑人市長！非常恭喜！。」"},{"pid":"ff8270e9985004ec1924fde96b808310ad1f65c1","tid":866523,"uid":3241,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T02:48:14.000Z","msg":"3成支持都冇....."},{"pid":"144355571b83af4c171a86bbd42113a7a8c69549","tid":866523,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T05:42:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi